text:
College mein to system ke chakkar mein bahut jhela yaar, ab real life mein bharat ke system ko badalne ke tumhare iraade ko humari taraf se laal salaam! Bas buerocracy mein phas ke mat reh jaana bhai..

Apni to bahut yaadein hain, Elections mein logon ko jitwaane se lekar nota se harwaane tak..galaxy mein 2nd year mein 3rd aane se 3rd year mein 1st aakar hall 3 ke saamne mootne tak..wo party gajab thi yaar, kya roast kiya tha logon ko daaru peeke..

Bundelkhand waalo ka up mein aana jaana laga rehta hai to hopefully jald milte hain!
 Jai shri Ram
